President Obama has issued a memorandum delegating certain functions under sections 1261(b) and 1262(a) of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2013. The functions under section 1261(b) are delegated to the Secretary of State, while the functions under section 1262(a) are delegated to the Secretary of Commerce. The Secretary of State is instructed to consult with other executive departments and agencies as necessary and is also authorized to publish the memorandum in the Federal Register.